window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>When You First Don't Succeed, Try and Try Again...</b></p> <p>With multiple enemy lords on each front, Matt has quite the challenge before him. Even with the multiple cities he's conquered, balancing the need for more units, future updates and traitorous lords is straining his patience and knowledge. Now, the enemy armies are coming, on all sides.</p> <p>And the only question is whether he can hold them off and push forward, before they overwhelm his defences.<br> <br> <i>Magic Kingdom at War </i>is a tactical, base-building, crunchy LitRPG novella series by Tao Wong, bestselling author of <i>the System Apocalypse, A Thousand Li, Climbing the Ranks,</i> the <i>Hidden Universe </i>and <i>Adventures on Brad </i>series.</p>"; 
